\s BWANA YESU
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Bwana Yesu Pendo lako ni kubwa Uliye nifiya kwa mu Msalabani shida nyingi zimenisonga Roho yangu Bwana Yesu Uniokowe.\bd*\bd x2\bd*\bd  \bd*
\pc \bdit Sasa(T) na sasa Bwana ninaimba nayo furaha Utukufuni mwako Bwana Yesu Roho mwili navitoa niwe makao yako Bwana.\bdit*\bdit x2\bdit*
\zon1 2
